(0, '537893', 'SIKKIM Valley of Flowers', 'Honeymoon', NULL, '83073', 'Domestic', '6', '5', 'SIKKIM Valley of Flowers', '14999', '00', 'Couple Only,Family Only,Friends,,Couple Only,,', '', '', 'Hotel,Dinner,Transfer PVT,Sightseeing,,,', '2 Star,,,', 'Others', 'tripasa.in', 'lifetime', 'Active', '1555666057.jpg', 'Sikkim is a state in northeast India, bordered by Bhutan, Tibet and Nepal. Part of the Himalayas, the area has a dramatic landscape that includes Indiaâ€™s highest mountain, 8,586m Kangchenjunga. Sikkim is also home to glaciers, alpine meadows and thousands of varieties of wildflowers. Steep paths lead to hilltop Buddhist monasteries such as Pemayangtse, which dates to the early 1700s.\r\nCapital: Gangtok\r\nGovernor: Ganga Prasad\r\nChief minister: Pawan Kumar Chamling\r\nPoints of interest: Lake Tsomgo, Rumtek Monastery, MORE\r\nDid you know: Sikkim is the third-highest-income Indian state / union territory  ', '2019-04-15 08:03:05', 'NA'),
(0, '590025', 'SOUTHERN TRIANGLE', 'Romantic', NULL, '89340', 'Domestic', '6', '5', 'SOUTHERN TRIANGLE', '00', '00', 'Couple Only,Family Only,,', '', '', 'Hotel,Dinner,Transfer PVT,Sightseeing,,', '2 Star,,', '', 'tripasa.in', 'lifetime', 'Active', '1555411203.png', 'Karnataka is a state in southwest India with Arabian Sea coastlines. The capital, Bengaluru (formerly Bangalore), is a high-tech hub known for its shopping and nightlife. To the southwest, Mysore is home to lavish temples including Mysore Palace, former seat of the regionâ€™s maharajas. Hampi, once the medieval Vijayanagara empireâ€™s capital, contains ruins of Hindu temples, elephant stables and a stone chariot.\r\nChief minister: H. D. Kumaraswamy\r\nGovernor: Vajubhai Vala\r\nCapital: Bengaluru (Executive Branch)\r\nPlan a trip\r\nKarnataka travel guide\r\n2 h 25 min flight\r\nPoints of interest: Mysore Palace, Lalbagh Botanical Garden, MORE\r\nDid you know: Karnataka has the 10th-highest life expectancy at birth (68.8) during 2010-14 among all Indian ', '2019-04-15 08:14:15', 'NA'),
