(0, '112786', 'EXPLORE THAILAND ', 'Weekend', NULL, '80207', 'International', '5', '4', 'EXPLORE THAILAND ', '19999', '00', 'Couple Only,Friends,Bachelor,,,,,', 'BANGKOK', 'Thailand', 'Hotel,Dinner,Transfer PVT,Sightseeing,,,,,', '3 Star,,,,,', 'Others', '484049,', 'lifetime', 'Active', '1557390970.pattaya-1024x768', 'Thailand is a Southeast Asian country. It\'s known for tropical beaches, opulent royal palaces, ancient ruins and ornate temples displaying figures of Buddha. In Bangkok, the capital, an ultramodern cityscape rises next to quiet canalside communities and the iconic temples of Wat Arun, Wat Pho and the Emerald Buddha Temple (Wat Phra Kaew). Nearby beach resorts include bustling Pattaya and fashionable Hua Hin.\r\nCapital: Bangkok\r\nDialing code: +66\r\nCurrency: Thai baht\r\nPoints of interest: The Grand Palace, Phi Phi Islands, Pa Tong, MORE\r\nOfficial language: Thai    ', '2019-04-15 16:49:31', 'NA'),
(0, '441061', 'DUBAI SAFARI', 'Winter', NULL, '75673', 'International', '5', '4', 'DUBAI SAFARI', '31999', '00', 'Group,Couple Only,Friends,Weekend,Bachelor,,,,', '', '', 'Hotel,Dinner,Transfer PVT,Criuse,Sightseeing,,,,', '3 Star,,,,', 'Others', 'tripasa.in', 'lifetime', 'Active', '1556783168.jpg', 'The United Arab Emirates is an Arabian Peninsula nation settled mainly along the Persian (Arabian) Gulf. The country is a federation of 7 emirates. Abu Dhabi, the island capital, is home to Sheikh Zayed Grand Mosque, with crystal chandeliers and room for 40,000 worshipers. Dubai is the site of ultramodern Burj Khalifa tower, enormous shopping centers and extravagant entertainment attractions.\r\nCapital: Abu Dhabi\r\nDialing code: +971\r\nCurrency: United Arab Emirates dirham\r\nPlan a trip\r\nUnited Arab Emirates travel guide\r\n8 h 15 min flight\r\nPoints of interest: Burj Khalifa, Burj Al Arab Jumeirah, MORE\r\nDid you know: United Arab Emirates has the 10th-highest economic freedom score (77.6) in the world based on the Economic Freedom of the World    ', '2019-04-15 17:04:51', 'NA'),
(0, '522070', 'SINGAPORE ', 'Summer', NULL, '14911', 'International', '5', '6', 'SINGAPORE TOUR', '29999', '00', 'Group,Couple Only,Family Only,Friends,Weekend,Bachelor,,,,', '', '', 'Hotel,Dinner,Transfer PVT,Sightseeing,,,,', '3 Star,,,,', 'Others', 'tripasa.in', 'lifetime', 'Active', '1555582762.jpg', 'Singapore, an island city-state off southern Malaysia, is a global financial center with a tropical climate and multicultural population. Its colonial core centers on the Padang, a cricket field since the 1830s and now flanked by grand buildings such as City Hall, with its 18 Corinthian columns. In Singapore\'s circa-1820 Chinatown stands the red-and-gold Buddha Tooth Relic Temple, said to house one of Buddha\'s teeth.\r\nDialing code: +65\r\nCurrency: Singapore dollar\r\nPopulation: 56.1 lakhs   ', '2019-04-15 17:24:37', 'NA'),
(0, '367085', 'MALAYSIA', 'Honeymoon', NULL, '26299', 'International', '4', '3', 'MALAYSIA TOUR ', '10999', '00', 'Group,Couple Only,Family Only,Friends,Weekend,Bachelor,,,,', '', '', 'Hotel,Dinner,Transfer PVT,Sightseeing,,,,', '3 Star,,,,', 'Others', 'tripasa.in', 'lifetime', 'Active', '1555582862.jpg', 'Malaysia is a Southeast Asian country occupying parts of the Malay Peninsula and the island of Borneo. It\'s known for its beaches, rainforests and mix of Malay, Chinese, Indian and European cultural influences. The capital, Kuala Lumpur, is home to colonial buildings, busy shopping districts such as Bukit Bintang and skyscrapers such as the iconic, 451m-tall Petronas Twin Towers.\r\nPrime minister: Mahathir Bin Mohamad Trending\r\nCapital: Kuala Lumpur\r\nDialing code: +60\r\nCurrency: Malaysian ringgit\r\nPlan a trip   ', '2019-04-15 17:35:01', 'NA'),
(0, '416985', 'Vietnam and Cambodia', 'Honeymoon', NULL, '69398', 'International', '13', '12', 'Vietnam and Cambodia', '68999', '00', 'Group,Couple Only,Family Only,Friends,Bachelor,,', '', '', 'Hotel,Dinner,Transfer PVT,Sightseeing,,', '3 Star,,', 'Others', 'tripasa.in', 'lifetime', 'Active', '1555915464.jpg', 'Cambodia is a Southeast Asian nation whose landscape spans low-lying plains, the Mekong Delta, mountains and Gulf of Thailand coastline. Phnom Penh, its capital, is home to the art deco Central Market, glittering Royal Palace and the National Museum\'s historical and archaeological exhibits. In the country\'s northwest are the ruins of Angkor Wat, a massive stone temple complex built during the Khmer Empire.\r\n\r\nVietnam is a Southeast Asian country on the South China Sea known for its beaches, rivers, Buddhist pagodas and bustling cities. Hanoi, the capital, pays homage to the nationâ€™s iconic Communist-era leader, Ho Chi Minh, via a huge marble mausoleum. Ho Chi Minh City (formerly Saigon) has French colonial landmarks, plus Vietnamese War history museums and the Cá»§ Chi tunnels, used by Viet Cong soldiers. ', '2019-04-16 02:06:00', 'NA'),
(0, '933033', 'BALI TOUR', 'Summer', NULL, '64676', 'International', '5', '4', 'BALI TOUR', '17999', '00', 'Group,Couple Only,Family Only,Friends,Weekend,Bachelor,,', '', '', 'Hotel,Dinner,Transfer PVT,Sightseeing,,', '3 Star,,', 'Others', '484049,', 'lifetime', 'Active', '1555669512.jpg', 'Indonesia, a Southeast Asian nation made up of thousands of volcanic islands, is home to hundreds of ethnic groups speaking many different languages. Itâ€™s known for beaches, volcanoes, Komodo dragons and jungles sheltering elephants, orangutans and tigers. On the island of Java lies Indonesia\'s vibrant, sprawling capital, Jakarta, and the city of Yogyakarta, known for gamelan music and traditional puppetry.\r\nPresident: Joko Widodo Trending\r\nCapital: Jakarta\r\nDialing code: +62\r\nCurrency: Indonesian rupiah ', '2019-04-16 02:30:57', 'NA'),
(0, '915246', 'Things of Gujarat', 'Weekend', NULL, '77896', 'Domestic', '8', '7', 'Things of Gujarat ', '29634', '00', 'Group,Family Only,Friends,Bachelor,', 'Gujarat', 'India', 'Hotel,Dinner,Transfer PVT,Sightseeing,', '3 Star,', '', 'Self', 'lifetime', 'Active', '1555914990.jpg', 'Gujarat, India\'s westernmost state, has varied terrain and numerous sacred sites. In its urban center of Ahmedabad is the Calico Museum of Textiles, displaying antique and modern Indian fabrics. Spiritual leader Mahatma Gandhi\'s base from 1917â€“1930 was Sabarmati Ashram, where his living quarters remain on view. The Jama Masjid (Friday Mosque), built in the 15th century, has a huge courtyard and a columned design.\r\nCapital: Gandhinagar\r\nChief minister: Vijay Rupani\r\nGovernor: Om Prakash Kohli\r\nPopulation: 6.27 crores (2013)', '2019-04-22 06:36:29', 'NA'),
(0, '905844', 'KERALA', 'Weekend', NULL, '43427', 'Domestic', '6', '5', 'KERALA', '17999', '00', 'Group,Family Only,Weekend,Bachelor,,', '', '', 'Hotel,Dinner,Transfer PVT,Sightseeing,,', '2 Star,,', 'Others', '484049,', 'lifetime', 'Active', '1558336451.jpg', 'Kerala\r\nState of India\r\nDescriptionKerala, a state on India\'s tropical Malabar Coast, has nearly 600km of Arabian Sea shoreline. It\'s known for its palm-lined beaches and backwaters, a network of canals. Inland are the Western Ghats, mountains whose slopes support tea, coffee and spice plantations as well as wildlife. National parks like Eravikulam and Periyar, plus Wayanad and other sanctuaries, are home to elephants, langur monkeys and tigers.\r\nCapital: Thiruvananthapuram\r\nChief minister: Pinarayi Vijayan\r\nPopulation: 3.48 crores (2012)\r\nPlan a trip\r\nKerala travel guide\r\n5 h 50 min flight\r\nPoints of interest: Thekkady, Eravikulam National Park, Fort Kochi, MORE\r\nDid you know: Kerala has the highest life expectancy at birth (76.3) during 2010-14 among all Indian ', '2019-04-22 07:11:28', 'NA'),
(0, '573081', 'SAI DARBAR', 'Honeymoon', NULL, '28915', 'Domestic', '4', '3', 'SAI DARBAR', '14999', '00', 'Family Only,', 'SHIRDI', 'India', 'Hotel,Dinner,Transfer PVT,Sightseeing,', '3 Star,', 'Others', '484049,', 'lifetime', 'Active', '1555918063.jpg', 'Sai Baba of Shirdi, also known as Shirdi Sai Baba, was an Indian spiritual master who is regarded by his devotees as a saint, a fakir, a satguru and an incarnation of Lord Shiva and Dattatreya. He is revered by both his Hindu and Muslim devotees during, as well as after his lifetime', '2019-04-22 07:27:42', 'NA'),
(0, '580808', 'BHAKTI YATRA', 'Weekend', NULL, '54594', 'Domestic', '5', '4', 'BHAKTI YATRA', '22000', '00', 'Family Only,,', '', '', 'Hotel,Transfer PVT,Sightseeing,,Dinner,', '2 Star,,', 'Others', '484049,', 'lifetime', 'Active', '1555919135.jpg', 'Haridwar is an ancient city and important Hindu pilgrimage site in North India\'s Uttarakhand state, where the River Ganges exits the Himalayan foothills. The largest of several sacred ghats (bathing steps), Har Ki Pauri hosts a nightly Ganga Aarti (river-worshipping ceremony) in which tiny flickering lamps are floated off the steps. Worshipers fill the city during major festivals including the annual Kanwar Mela.\r\nElevation: 314 m\r\nArea: 12.3 kmÂ²\r\nPopulation: 2.29 lakhs (2011)\r\nLocal time: Monday, 1:02 pm\r\nWeather: 33 Â°C, Wind W at 8 km/h, 34% Humidity ', '2019-04-22 07:39:54', 'NA'),
