(0, '676558', 'KRABI CITY BREAK', 'Weekend', NULL, '59682', 'International', '3', '2', 'KRABI CITY BREAK', '4500', '00', 'Couple Only,Family Only,Friends,Weekend,Bachelor,,,', '', '', 'Hotel,Dinner,Transfer PVT,Sightseeing,,,', '3 Star,,,', 'Others', 'tripasa.in', 'lifetime', 'Active', '1558704227.', 'Krabi is the main town in the province of Krabi on the west coast of southern Thailand at the mouth of the Krabi River where it empties in Phang Nga Bay. As of 2010 the town had a population of 52,867. The town is the capital of Krabi Province and Krabi District. Tourism is an important industry.  ', '2019-05-08 10:32:29', 'NA'),
(0, '827022', 'BALI TOUR', 'Honeymoon', NULL, '64676', 'International', '6', '5', 'BALI TOUR', '25000', '00', 'Couple Only,Family Only,Weekend,', 'BALI', 'Indonesia', 'Hotel,Dinner,Transfer PVT,Sightseeing,', '4 Star,', 'Others', '484049,', 'lifetime', 'Active', '1557391486.jpg', 'Bali is an Indonesian island known for its forested volcanic mountains, iconic rice paddies, beaches and coral reefs. The island is home to religious sites such as cliffside Uluwatu Temple. To the south, the beachside city of Kuta has lively bars, while Seminyak, Sanur and Nusa Dua are popular resort towns. The island is also known for its yoga and meditation retreats.\r\nArea: 5,780 kmÂ²\r\nCapital: Denpasar', '2019-05-09 08:44:45', 'NA'),
(0, '958051', 'GANGTOK // KALIMPONG ', 'Summer', NULL, '36791', 'Domestic', '6', '5', 'GANGTOK // KALIMPONG ', '24700', '00', 'Couple Only,Family Only,Friends,Bachelor,', 'Guwahati â€“Shillong--Dirangâ€“ Tawang', 'India', 'Hotel,Dinner,Transfer PVT,Sightseeing,', '3 Star,', '', '484049,', 'lifetime', 'Active', '1558787057.jpeg', 'Sikkim is a state in northeast India, bordered by Bhutan, Tibet and Nepal. Part of the Himalayas, the area has a dramatic landscape that includes Indiaâ€™s highest mountain, 8,586m Kangchenjunga. Sikkim is also home to glaciers, alpine meadows and thousands of varieties of wildflowers. Steep paths lead to hilltop Buddhist monasteries such as Pemayangtse, which dates to the early 1700s. Capital: Gangtok Governor: Ganga Prasad Chief minister: Pawan Kumar Chamling Points of interest: Lake Tsomgo, Rumtek Monastery, MORE Did you know: Sikkim is the third-highest-income Indian state / union territory', '2019-05-25 12:24:17', 'NA'),
(0, '419962', 'LUXURY HONEYMOON ', 'Honeymoon', NULL, '92102', 'International', '5', '4', 'MALDIVES ', '46999', '00', 'Couple Only,', 'MALDIVES ', 'Maldives', 'Hotel,Lunch,Dinner,Transfer PVT,Sightseeing,', '4 Star,', 'Others', '484049,', 'lifetime', 'Active', '1558947023.jpg', 'Escape to an exotic world of breathtaking possibility, where adventure and relaxation are equally within reach. At Sun Island Resort & Spa â€“ a flowering jewel among Maldives family hotels â€“ every moment is free to shape into your personal version of paradise. Cruise along our stunning sapphire lagoons by jet-ski, canoe, windsurf or catamaran. Explore the spectacular local scenery and unique Maldivian culture with excursions to neighbouring islands. Or, simply let the ocean breeze caress you to sleep as you sway gently in your hammock. From invigorating activities to precious tranquillity, our Maldives fun island resort will captivate the heart with extraordinary experiences and unforgettable memories', '2019-05-27 08:50:22', 'NA'),
(0, '615921', 'JAPAN TOUR', 'Summer', NULL, '27998', 'International', '7', '6', 'JAPAN TOUR', '99720', '00', 'Couple Only,Family Only,Friends,,', 'Tokyo-Mt.Fujiâ€“Hakoneâ€“Osakaâ€“Kyoto-Nara', 'Japan', 'Hotel,Transfer,Guide,Sightseeing,', '3 Star,,', 'Others', '484049,', 'lifetime', 'Active', '1559028784.', 'Japan is an island country in East Asia. Located in the Pacific Ocean, it lies off the eastern coast of the Asian continent and stretches from the Sea of Okhotsk in the north to the East China Sea and the Philippine Sea in the south.\r\nEmperor: Naruhito Trending\r\nCapital: Tokyo\r\nCurrency: Japanese yen\r\nPopulation: 12.68 crores (2017) World Bank ', '2019-05-27 11:30:53', 'NA'),
(0, '590790', 'China', 'Summer', NULL, '68939', 'International', '7', '6', 'China along with India, Egypt and Mesopotamia (modern Iraq and Iran) is an ancient civilization aged more than 5,000 years old. The Chinese culture features an abundance of the material and spiritual values, unchanged over millennia. ... Of special note is Chinese written language.', '85999', '00', 'Couple Only,Family Only,Friends,', 'BEIJING', 'China', 'Air,Hotel,Lunch,Dinner,Transfer SIC,Guide,Sightseeing,', '3 Star,4 Star,', 'Others', '484049,', 'lifetime', 'Active', '1559041673.jpg', 'China, officially the People\'s Republic of China (PRC), is a country in East Asia and the world\'s most populous country, with a population of around 1.404 billion.[10] Covering approximately 9,600,000 square kilometers (3,700,000 sq mi), it is the third- or fourth-largest country by total area.[k][16] Governed by the Communist Party of China, the state exercises jurisdiction over 22 provinces, five autonomous regions, four direct-controlled municipalities (Beijing, Tianjin, Shanghai, and Chongqing), and the special administrative regions of Hong Kong and Macau.', '2019-05-28 11:07:52', 'NA'),
