('446077', 1, 'NA', 'NA', 'NA', '.Upon arrival in Guwahati, meet our tour representative whoâ€™ll assist you in smooth transfer to the hotel for overnight stay. ', 'NA', 'NA', 'Active'),
('446077', 2, 'NA', 'NA', 'NA', '.Post breakfast in the morning, pay a visit to the Kamakhya Temple, a major Hindu pilgrimage site. One of the famous Shakti peethas in the North East India, Kamakhya temple is visited by a million devotees during the Ambubashi festival.Guwahuti zoo ,drive to hotel and take some rest. Then in the late evening you can go for River Cruise in the mighty river Brahmaputra or can visit local market. Rest in the time in leisure. Overnight stay at the Hotel in Guwahati\r\n', 'NA', 'NA', 'Active'),
('446077', 3, 'NA', 'NA', 'NA', '.Post breakfast, take a road journey to Shillong, also known as the â€˜Scotland of the Eastâ€™. On the way, visit the Elephanta falls and head straight to Shillong peak to enjoy some  breathtaking views. Overnight stay in Shillong. ', 'NA', 'NA', 'Active'),
('446077', 4, 'NA', 'NA', 'NA', '.After breakfast time permits visit Crystal lake. Cathedral of Marry and Wardâ€™s Lake. Evening free at leisure to explore the region on own. You may take a walk to the famous Police Bazaar for shopping. Overnight in Shillong. ', 'NA', 'NA', 'Active'),
('446077', 5, 'NA', 'NA', 'NA', '.After breakfast drive to Cherrapunjee, the wettest place on the earth, for an awesome day trip. En route visit the famous Elephant Falls and Shillong Peak - to enjoy a birdâ€™s eye view of Shillong city. At Sohra, stop at the Duwan Sing Syiem view point for mesmerizing views of the Hills In Cherrapunjee be witness to the gorgeous Seven Sisters Falls and Nohkalikai Falls. Later take a soft cave walk inside the Mawsmai Cave. The limestone cave is a natural wonder with innumerable formations inside it. After lunch at Cherrapunjee, visit Thankarang Park,', 'NA', 'NA', 'Active'),
('446077', 6, 'NA', 'NA', 'NA', '. Today, you will be transferred to the Guwahati airport to board flight for onward journey. ', 'NA', 'NA', 'Active'),
('395223', 1, 'NA', 'NA', 'NA', '.Arrive Guwahati â€“ Shillong (150km / 3h)\r\n\r\nMeet and greet upon arrival by our representative and then transfer to Shillong. The â€˜Gleneagles of the Eastâ€™ lies in the centre of a plateau surrounded by Khasi hills. Overnight in Shillong.', 'NA', 'NA', 'Active'),
('395223', 2, 'NA', 'NA', 'NA', '.Shillong Full Day Sightseeing\r\n\r\nAfter Breakfast, full day sightseeing of Shillong. Enroute sightseeing includes: Don Bosco Museum of Indigenous Culture, Wardâ€™s Lake, Botanical Garden, Lady Hydari Park, Golf Course, Elephant Falls, Shillong Peak. Later come back to hotel. Overnight in Shillong.', 'NA', 'NA', 'Active'),
('395223', 3, 'NA', 'NA', 'NA', '.Shillong â€“ Cherrapunjee â€“ Shillong (190 kms)\r\n\r\nAfter Breakfast, excursion to Cherrapunjee. Enroute sightseeing includes: Ramakrishna School and Museum, Eco Park, Nohsngithiang Falls, Nohkalikai Waterfalls, Mawkdok Dympep Valley View, Dainthlen Waterfalls. Overnight in Shillong.', 'NA', 'NA', 'Active'),
('395223', 4, 'NA', 'NA', 'NA', '.Shillong â€“ Mawlynnong - Dawki - Shillong\r\n\r\nAfter breakfast, excursion to Dawki (Tamabil â€“ Indo Bangladesh Border and Umngot River), en-route visit Mawlynnong. Overnight accommodation will be in Shillong', 'NA', 'NA', 'Active'),
('395223', 5, 'NA', 'NA', 'NA', '.Shillong - Bhalukpong\r\n\r\nAfter Breakfast, transfer from Shillong to Bhalukpong. En-route cross River Brahmaputra through the Bhumuraguri Bridge and Nameri National Park. Overnight accommodation will be in Bhalukpong.', 'NA', 'NA', 'Active'),
('395223', 6, 'NA', 'NA', 'NA', '.Bhalukpong - Dirang\r\n\r\nAfter Breakfast you will transfer to another Heaven on Earth location which is Dirang. On the way you will be visiting to Tipi Orchid Sanctuary and Research Centre. Overnight accommodation will be in Dirang.', 'NA', 'NA', 'Active'),
('395223', 7, 'NA', 'NA', 'NA', '.Dirangâ€“ Tawang (190 kms / 6.30h)\r\n\r\nAfter breakfast transfer to Tawang. While going to Tawang you will be visiting: Jaswant Garh, Sella Pass and Nurarang Falls. Overnight accommodation will be in Tawang.', 'NA', 'NA', 'Active'),
('395223', 8, 'NA', 'NA', 'NA', '.Tawang - Bumla pass - Tawang\r\n\r\nAfter Breakfast you will be having second full day sightseeing of Tawang. Today you will be driven to the McMohan Line (Line of Control â€“ Indo China) and Sangestser Lake, Pangateng Tso Lake (P.T. Tso Lake). Later come back to Tawang.', 'NA', 'NA', 'Active'),
('395223', 9, 'NA', 'NA', 'NA', '.Tawang - Bomdila\r\n\r\nAfter Breakfast transfer from Tawang to Bomdila. En-route visit Nurarang / Jung Falls, Bomdila Monastery, Also visit Craft Center. Overnight accommodation will be in Bomdila.', 'NA', 'NA', 'Active'),
