('395223', 11, 'NA', 'NA', 'NA', '.Guwahati Full Day Sightseeing\r\n\r\nAfter breakfast, it will be a full day sightseeing of Guwahati. Among the city sightseeing Second world war Cemetery, State Museum, State Zoo and Botanical Garden, Srimanta Sankardeva Kalakshetra (A museum of Assam diverse culture), and Regional Science Museum. Among the Temples are - Maa Kamakhya temple, Navagraha Temple, Bashistha Ashram. Tirupathi Balaji and you can also visit Umananda Island (The smallest inhabited island of India) â€“ There is a Shiva temple in the island and the only way to go there is a ferry.\r\n\r\nOvernight accommodation will be in Guwahati.\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nOptional: Sunset Brahmaputra River Cruise\r\n\r\n', 'NA', 'NA', 'Active'),
('395223', 12, 'NA', 'NA', 'NA', '.Guwahati Full Day Sightseeing\r\n\r\nAfter Breakfast, transfer to Guwahati Airport / Railway station for your departure', 'NA', 'NA', 'Active'),
('112786', 1, 'NA', 'NA', 'NA', '.Suvarnabhumi Airport - Hotel (Bangkok)\r\nWelcome to Bangkok. Upon arrival at the airport you will be met by our local representative who will transfer you to hotel.\r\nEnroute Sriacha Tiger Zoo.\r\nMake a visit to the incredible Sriracha Tiger Zoo, the biggest\r\n tiger zoo in Asia located in Pattaya\r\nSee over 300 Panthera Tigris and nearly 100,000 species of \r\ncrocodiles on site Meet, greet, and feed adorable tiger cubs, \r\nfarm animals, \r\nostriches, kangaroos, and more \r\nVisit a zoo that promotes the protection of the environment \r\nand various endangered animals\r\n\r\nRUSSION SHOW :-fantasy show of lady russian \r\nmore beautiful body.Dancing sing a song , \r\nshower show , more sexy can by ticket with us \r\nto see show every day.\r\n\r\n', 'NA', 'NA', 'Active'),
('112786', 2, 'NA', 'NA', 'NA', '.Coral Island Tour with Lunch by Speed Boat (Pattaya)\r\nCoral Island Tour with Lunch by Speed Boat â€“ \r\nWW market[Enjoy Parasailing, under sea  walk, Scooter driving (Own Cost).]\r\nInclusions:\r\npvt Transfers from Cetrally located hotel\r\nEntry Tickets\r\nSeafood Lunch\r\nPVT VEHICLE BASIS, should not be considered as vehicle at disposal. \r\nIt only means that you are not sharing the vehicle with any other guests.\r\nMeals: Breakfast, Lunch \r\n', 'NA', 'NA', 'Active'),
('112786', 3, 'NA', 'NA', 'NA', '.Half  Day free time to leasure in pattya  (No Services included) (pattya )\r\nThere is no service included, you may spend time, as per your interests\r\n\r\n\r\n69 show in Pattaya (X-Show)    \r\nIt is high time you see a show for adults which is well-known all over \r\nthe world. The performance takes\r\n place on the stage. You wonâ€™t have a chance to see \r\n such show in any other country of the world.\r\n', 'NA', 'NA', 'Active'),
('112786', 4, 'NA', 'NA', 'NA', '.Full Day Safari World Marine Park with Lunch (Bangkok)\r\nNo one can resist the excitement of indulging in a day full of  \r\nexperiences and activities at safari world & marine park. Witness the\r\n majestic wild creatures like African lion and Bengal tiger on a\r\n 8 km long drive, then pass through the most beautiful and fun\r\n loving animals like Orangutan,dolphins and colorful bird species. \r\nEnjoy watching the Dolphins performanceHighlights\r\nâ€¢The park is unique for as it blends the Wild & Herbivorous \r\nAnimals with the Exotic Fresh Water and Oceanic Life\r\nâ€¢The diverse species of animals will amaze you who are \r\nliving in this natural like habitat\r\nâ€¢See walrus, orangutan, kangaroo, monkey, crocodile, tapir, all kinds of tropical birds, giant fish and Much More\r\nâ€¢Mesmerize yourself by witnessing the friendly Dolphins performing somersaults\r\nâ€¢Orang Utan Boxing Show - Man\'s closest cousins take center stage as they tickle you with their keen sense of humor and dazzle you with their mathematical gifts.\r\nInclusions:\r\nTransfers from Cetrally located hotels/ Entrance tickets/Lunch\r\n', 'NA', 'NA', 'Active'),
('112786', 5, 'NA', 'NA', 'NA', '.Half Day Chao Phraya Princess Cruise with Dinner (Bangkok)\r\nExperience Bangkok by night aboard this cruise \r\n(Chao Phraya Princess) that will take you along the \r\nChao Phraya River. See twoof Bangkokâ€™s most famous attractions \r\nilluminated in the night â€“ Wat Arun (Temple of Dawn) and the\r\n Grand Palace (Official residence of the King of Thailand). Sit back and \r\nrelax while feasting on Indian and Thai delicacies and enjoy the \r\nmagnificent skyline of Bangkok.\r\nInclusions:\r\nTransfers from Cetrally located hotels\r\nEntrance tickets\r\nDinner\r\n\r\nBangkok â€“ Over night  proceed  to SUVARNBHUMI  AIRPORT TRANSFER â€“ PVT \r\n\r\n\r\n', 'NA', 'NA', 'Active'),
