('915246', 2, 'NA', 'NA', 'NA', '.Ahmedabad â€“ Jamnagar â€“ Dwarka (450 kms/09 hrs)\r\n\r\nToday, proceed to Jamnagar. On arrival visit Lakhota Lake & Lakhota Museum. In the evening, visit Bala Hanuman Temple known for its nonstop Ramdhun since 1956 and it mentioned in Guinness Book of World Records. Latter proceed to the sacred town of Dwarka. Overnight stay at the hotel.\r\n', 'NA', 'NA', 'Active'),
('915246', 3, 'NA', 'NA', 'NA', '.Dwarka Excursion\r\n\r\nToday,. Visit Dwarkadeesh Temple. Take a holy dip in Gomti river, later leave to visit Nageshwar Jyotirling, Gopi Talav, Bet Dwarka, and on way back do visit Rukmani Temple, evening visit other temples on coastal area, attend evening aarti at Dwarkadish temple. Overnight stay at the hotel.\r\n', 'NA', 'NA', 'Active'),
('915246', 4, 'NA', 'NA', 'NA', '.: Dwarka â€“ Porbandar â€“ Somnath (250 kms/05 hrs)\r\n\r\nIn the morning depart to Porbandar (75km/1.5hrs) at Porbandar visit Kirti Mandir â€“ the place where Gandhiji was born and Sudama Temple â€“ The only Sudama Temple in the world. Later proceed to Somnath (130km/2.5hrs) on arrival visit Bhalka Tirth, Triveni Sagam, Geeta Mandir Chopati & Somnath Temple. In the evening attend Aarti and later watch light and Sound show. Overnight stay at the hotel.\r\n', 'NA', 'NA', 'Active'),
('915246', 5, 'NA', 'NA', 'NA', '.â€“ Sasan Gir (50 kms/01 hrs)\r\n\r\nAfter breakfast Proceed to Sasangir. Sasangir, is the home of the Asiatic Lion. Visit Gir Interpretation Zone at Devaliya (Closed on Wednesday) Later, get ready for open jeep safari at Gir National Park. Overnight stay at the hotel.\r\n', 'NA', 'NA', 'Active'),
('915246', 6, 'NA', 'NA', 'NA', '.Sasan Gir â€“ Diu (100 kms/02 hrs)\r\n\r\nToday, after breakfast proceed to beach town Diu. Later, visit St. Paul\'s Church, Diu Museum and Diu Fort.\r\n\r\nEvening is at leisure to laze and relax on the beach. Overnight stay at the hotel.\r\n', 'NA', 'NA', 'Active'),
