('573081', 1, 'NA', 'NA', 'NA', '.Arrive MUMBAI   to  SHIRDI\r\n\r\nUpon arrival at Mumbai   airport., Welcome by our representative at the Airport drive to Shirdi. On arrival and check in Hotel. Attend the Aarti ceremony which usually takes place by 6 PM. Overnight at Hotel in Shirdi.', 'NA', 'NA', 'Active'),
('573081', 2, 'NA', 'NA', 'NA', '.SHIRDI\r\n\r\nEarly Morning visit Samadhi Mandir for Darshan. Later Visit Dwarkamai Masjid, Chawri, Khandoba Temple and Shani Shingnapur. By evening attend Aarti ceremony in Shirdi. Overnight at Hotel in Shirdi.', 'NA', 'NA', 'Active'),
