('979695', 3, 'NA', 'NA', 'NA', '.Early morning Fly Simikot- Hilsa then  Drive to Purang( Taklakot)\r\nEarly morning you will be transfer to domestic airlines to take the flight to simkot with packed breakfast \r\nUpon reaching Simikot airport take a Helicopter \r\nFlight to Hilsa\r\nFresh up at local guest house with tea/coffee. Then crossing Karnali bridge arrives to Chinese land. Drive to Purang (Taklakot). Before Purang have immigration formalities at Chinese custom office. \r\nDrive to Purang  ( Taklakot)\r\n\r\nDinner & Overnight at Hotel ', 'NA', 'NA', 'Active'),
