('657038', 2, 'NA', 'NA', 'NA', '.Full Day Phi Phi Island Tour by Speed Boat (Phuket)\r\nPhi Phi Islands, located just 45 minutes by speedboat from Phuket, offer a great laid back \r\ntropical life style. Soak up the sun, go beach hopping or simply enjoy the great outdoors in some of the most beautiful scenery in Asia.\r\nClassic white sandy beaches, surrounded by impressive limestone cliffs and \r\nsunlit crystal clear water, Phi Phi actually consist of two islands, \r\nPhi Phi Don and Phi Phi Ley Monkey Beach.\r\nInclusions:\r\nTransfers from Areas-Patong, Kata, Karon (If Hotel booked in any\r\n other location private supplement will be charged ).\r\nRoundtrip Speed boat transfer\r\nGuest have to pay national park fees on the spot\r\n\r\nMeal-Breakfast  . Buffet Lunch', 'NA', 'NA', 'Active'),
('657038', 3, 'NA', 'NA', 'NA', '.Hotel - Phuket International Airport (Phuket)\r\nCheck out from hotel and get transferred to the airport for your journey to further destination .\r\n\r\n\r\nHotel - Phuket International Airport (Phuket)\r\nSuvarnabhumi Airport - Hotel (pattaya)\r\nWelcome to Bangkok. Upon arrival at the airport you will be met by our local representative who will transfer you topattaya hotel.\r\n\r\nHalf Day Alcazar Show Regular Seat (Pattaya)\r\nCatch the greatest show in Asia and be mesmerized by the extravagant costumes,\r\n stunning ladyboys and grand stage sets that display larger than life performances! \r\nThe Alcazar Show has all the glitz and glamour of a Las Vegas nightclub\r\n. Performed in a state of the art theatre, the show uses the latest technology\r\n to deliver a fabulous show!\r\n\r\nMeal-Breakfast  , ', 'NA', 'NA', 'Active');
